  "description": "Based on the events of the Three Kingdoms era in China (3rd century), and on Luo Guanzhong's famous novel <i>Sanguo Yanyi</i>, the game casts the player in the role of one of the many warlords rivaling for control after the Yellow Turban Rebellion.<br><br>This turn-based strategy game introduces hundreds of historical characters of the Three Kingdoms era. The game's main objective is to become the supreme ruler of the remnants of the falling Han Dynasty. To do this the player has to build a mighty empire by conquering provinces and recruiting generals worthy of command. Fight massive battles, triumph over natural disasters and capture enemy strongholds.",
